{
  "texts": [
    "For example, a participant in a study [G1] perceived that every AI system has some ethical issues initially and they take actions to either avoid or mitigate them.",
    "In a similar vein, a few participants in studies such as [G12], [G14], and [G34] reported that AI systems will always have some biases as humans create those systems.",
    "ɓ \"The machine will always have biases, always being created by a programmer, and the programmer has prejudices.\"",
    "-AI expert-[G12].",
    "ɓ \"There is always a risk that the translation (AI) can be biased.\""
  ]
}